{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"predicate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"predicate","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNVectorStyleLayer(py)predicate","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"predicate","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer\/predicate"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSPredicate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSPredicate"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use the style layer’s predicate to include only the features in the source"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer that satisfy a condition that you define. If the style layer initially"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"comes from the style, its predicate corresponds to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"filter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in the style JSON."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See the “"},{"type":"text","text":"Predicates and Expressions"},{"type":"text","text":"”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guide for details about the predicate syntax supported by this class."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Example","level":3,"text":"Example","